#. module: dev_loan_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:dev_loan_management.installment_reminder_email_template
msgid ""
"\n"
"            \n"
"                <p>Dear <strong><t t-out=\"object.client_id.name\"/></strong>,</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>We would like to remind you of the upcoming installment for your loan\n"
"                <strong><t t-out=\"object.loan_id.name\"/></strong>. Below are the details:</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <ul>\n"
"                    <li><strong>Installment Number:</strong> <t t-out=\"object.name\"/></li>\n"
"                    <li><strong>Due Date:</strong> <t t-out=\"object.date\"/></li>\n"
"                    <li><strong>Amount Due:</strong> <t t-out=\"object.total_amount\"/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.currency_id.symbol\"/></li>\n"
"                </ul>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Please make the payment promptly. If you have already paid, kindly ignore this message.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Thank you for your cooperation.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p><strong>Regards,</strong><br/>\n"
"                <strong><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"/></strong></p>\n"
"            \n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<p>Prezado <strong><t t-out=\"object.client_id.name\"/></strong>,</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Gostaríamos de lembrá-lo da próxima parcela do seu empréstimo\n"
"                <strong><t-out=\"object.loan_id.name\"/></strong>. Abaixo estão os detalhes:</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <ul>\n"
"                    <li><strong>Número da parcela:</strong> <t t-out=\"object.name\"/></li>\n"
"                    <li><strong>Data de vencimento:</strong> <t t-out=\"object.date\"/></li>\n"
"                    <li><strong>Valor devido:</strong> <t t-out=\"object.total_amount\"/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.currency_id.symbol\"/></li>\n"
"                </ul>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Por favor, faça o pagamento imediatamente. Se você já pagou, ignore esta mensagem.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Obrigado pela sua cooperação.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p><strong>Atenciosamente,</strong><br/>\n"
"                <strong><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"/></strong></p>"

