#. module: dev_loan_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:dev_loan_management.template_overdue_installment_send_by_mail
msgid ""
"<p>\n"
"                Dear\n"
"                <t t-out=\"object.client_id.name\"></t>,\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>We hope this message finds you well. We would like to bring to your attention that your loan installment due on <strong><t t-out=\"object.date\"></t></strong> remains unpaid. Below are the details of the overdue installment:</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <table style=\"width:100%; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Loan Number</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.loan_id.name\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Loan Type</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.loan_id.loan_type_id.name\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Installment Number</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.name\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">EMI</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.currency_id.symbol\"></t> <t t-out=\"object.total_amount\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Date</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.date\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"            </table>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>We kindly request you to make the payment at the earliest to avoid additional penalties or disruption to your loan agreement.</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>If you have already made the payment, please ignore this message. If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact us at <strong><t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"></t></strong> or call us at <strong><t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"></t></strong>.</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>Best regards,<br>\n"
"            The <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t> Team</p>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<p>\n"
"                Querido\n"
"                <t t-out=\"object.client_id.name\"></t>,\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>Esperamos que esta mensagem o encontre bem. Gostaríamos de chamar sua atenção para o fato de que a parcela do seu empréstimo com vencimento em <strong><t t-out=\"object.date\"></t></strong> ainda não foi paga. Segue abaixo o detalhamento da parcela vencida:</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <table style=\"largura:100%; borda: 1px sólido #ddd; border-collapse: colapso;\">\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Número do empréstimo</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px sólido #ddd; preenchimento: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.loan_id.name\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Tipo de empréstimo</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px sólido #ddd; preenchimento: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.loan_id.loan_type_id.name\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Número da parcela</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px sólido #ddd; preenchimento: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.name\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px sólido #ddd; preenchimento: 8px;\">EMI</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px sólido #ddd; preenchimento: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.currency_id.symbol\"></t> <t t-out=\"object.total_amount\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"                <tr>\n"
"                    <th style=\"text-align: left; border: 1px sólido #ddd; preenchimento: 8px;\">Data</th>\n"
"                    <td style=\"border: 1px sólido #ddd; preenchimento: 8px;\"><t t-out=\"object.date\"></t></td>\n"
"                </tr>\n"
"            </tabela>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>Solicitamos que você efetue o pagamento o mais rápido possível para evitar penalidades adicionais ou interrupção do seu contrato de empréstimo.</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>Se você já efetuou o pagamento, ignore esta mensagem. Se você tiver alguma dúvida ou precisar de ajuda, sinta-se à vontade para entrar em contato conosco em <strong><t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"></t></strong> ou ligue para <strong><t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"></t></strong>.</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>Agradecemos sua pronta atenção a este assunto.</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>Atenciosamente,<br>\n"
"            A <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t> Equipe</p>"

